Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們活著追求幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神就是將點滴的幸福分給這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.81,0:01:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後那人的笑容又拯救了女神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是接受了女神們的愛的男人的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:02:02.89,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HC37281&\3c&HCDE9F0&\be1}啊 許願吧 再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從自知自身不成熟\N再次踏上旅途已過了11個月零3天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.05,0:02:28.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是為了像蓓兒丹蒂大人那樣讓眾人幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我淨化著自己的心靈\N追求著歌唱的心靈持續著旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有歌聲的地方我都會踏足
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:43.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就是回來報告修行成果的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.78,0:02:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 還真是乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.78,0:02:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺廟也很高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.69,0:02:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就去打個招呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我絕對饒不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:05.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說得好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是小看人家的發明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.14,0:03:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是有好好幫到姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別突然出現在人家面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你把我調和的寶貴的一見鍾情藥給打翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.01,0:03:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  把我的集束合成爆彈弄壞的是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了聽我說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所欠缺的是愛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.01,0:03:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就讓你們聽聽愛的歌聲…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電光召喚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番兵機雷發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 一個人在那嘮嘮叨叨的生什麼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 剛才就在人家的院子裏吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼 小丫頭 這裏是我的寺廟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 穿得那麼輕薄心靈也墮落了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.07,0:03:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 聽我唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後拋棄煩惱到我的胸膛來…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的修行還不夠…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣沒臉見蓓兒丹蒂大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.26,0:04:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要再去修行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.59,0:04:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼吵鬧沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概又是兀兒德和詩寇蒂在吵架了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這姐妹吵架還真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她們倆關係非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像螢一和惠一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 小螢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.65,0:04:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再沒這樣為你著想的妹妹了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你再客氣點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.52,0:04:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是在想因為有我在所以無法兩人獨處了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.47,0:04:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡人多熱鬧的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小螢也不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 小螢住到這裏也快一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.67,0:05:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從與螢一結下簽約之日起已經過了那麼久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.31,0:05:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們之間還有這樣的關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們是根據天上界的契約…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂她們的行動 消滅了究極破壞程序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因封印冥府之門失去的數據
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.75,0:05:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去不可修復的5%都恢復正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 製造了多餘的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次損壞的數據是助人女神事務所的登陸文件
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂這樣還能留在地上界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指契約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:08.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.65,0:06:13.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大魔王的事故讓她留在地上界也是有限度的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有天要讓她回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.39,0:06:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是笠原教授的講課
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要出門了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 到大學去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是森裏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是我」 請問是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:58.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.26,0:07:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是契約者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.14,0:07:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打 打給螢一？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:15.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在契約已經消滅 我也不能讓女神長時間留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大魔王給你帶來了麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會為你考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.89,0:07:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只給你整理心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說了這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是因為大魔王 消滅它的可是那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.46,0:07:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一沒有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:40.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是天神大人特意和我聯繫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:46.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是決定現在就要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在天上界工作的助人女神事務所並不只有我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想並不會人手不足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:08:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有螢一的願望被消滅掉 總覺得不能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:07.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把大魔王怎麼來著消滅掉的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 你是說是我的緣故嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被大魔王支配了還很高興地在城裏搞破壞的又是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就想消滅這事實
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.98,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消滅不了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到一點碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但關鍵的聲音數據破損嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能修復這個的話就可能修復
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要契約者的聲紋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:34.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.05,0:08:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯絡他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能修復嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將螢一的願望再次輸入系統就能修復文件了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一 你沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.95,0:09:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你緊張什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這很簡單吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音屏幕確認
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.74,0:09:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請講話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望像你這樣的女神一直留在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能通過認證 請再說一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.44,0:09:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我希望像你這樣的女神一直留在我身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能通過認證 可能是詞彙錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.20,0:09:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:46.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會忘了自己許的願啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該是這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望像你這樣的女神一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.74,0:09:53.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想有像你這樣的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃你做的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起去參觀博物館怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能說出那麼多還真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.22,0:10:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是有錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.82,0:10:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破損到無法通過聲音認證嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.55,0:10:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 蓓兒丹蒂 你不是記錄下密碼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.72,0:10:16.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為被加上了防護 所以我是不能說出密碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用這恢復記憶錘子和…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德大人特製記憶恢復藥劑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你選哪一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我現在在想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這樣快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 竟然忘了和姐姐的約定 真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是用爆雷降臨好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用番兵君特別攻擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了在做這個之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.73,0:10:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聽聽螢一是怎麼說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.76,0:11:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一 去大學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這時候了還去大學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候就需要轉換心情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:11.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.63,0:11:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想不用太在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.89,0:11:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契約的消滅並不是螢一的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能這樣和你一起上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能打上工也都是因為那個願望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此 現在才能像這樣在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我竟然忘了那個願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:12:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我是不懂關於這個內燃機的燃燒率…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.71,0:12:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.26,0:12:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是自動車部部員竟然連這個都不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是自動車部的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.32,0:12:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道廉恥嗎 廉恥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那今天就好好地教導你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:12.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.06,0:12:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了…我之後還要打工
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.46,0:12:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我們還要打工 先行告退了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.96,0:12:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算呆在地上界也解決不了問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能介入主系統調出密碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做可是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也是在盡力而為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.07,0:12:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是知道會亂來才回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個熱一下就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.07,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為螢一說了想兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們獨處的時間所剩不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣想的 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩寇蒂的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.73,0:13:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能侵入主數據庫 從姐姐的記憶文件中讀取密碼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能完成這個黑客君的話沒什麼不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼做這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:13:59.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是為螢一的事在擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣那個沒用可憐蟲螢一就會說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩寇蒂幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許還會被姐姐誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 再努力一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.84,0:14:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.03,0:14:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.12,0:14:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:27.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.98,0:14:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她總是在微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也必須給她回應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想看到蓓兒丹蒂的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是星期天 天又那麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們兩人出門逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.96,0:15:10.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…還沒有決定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和蓓兒丹蒂約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的時間我想好好地使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去做便當
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.71,0:15:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:38.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦說了是約會就緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有那種勇氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天是約會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:16:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你邀請我約會這是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.84,0:16:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今天就開心地渡過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算裝模作樣也沒用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.67,0:16:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連牽手都做不到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…這樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了收集螢一的聲音資料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風景真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然蓓兒丹蒂的微笑最漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.67,0:16:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.82,0:16:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝 一共是600日元
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天付煤氣費把上個月的打工錢用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一 不介意的話就請用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:01.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候作為男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的打工錢我還沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就讓我來付好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.82,0:17:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方吃便當真不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:26.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.01,0:17:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還能這樣多約會幾次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來去展望台吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏風景更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要牽個手…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:17:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛舞吧精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以吾之名集結  拯救他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 讓你救了不少次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:19:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也是 我到頭來什麼都為你做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.83,0:19:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.83,0:19:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一總是為在我著想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我忘記我是因為事務所的契約才留在螢一身邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和蓓兒丹蒂永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.07,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有這份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能再次在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.13,0:19:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.18,0:19:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想還會再見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.71,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是今後就見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果螢一需要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思念也一定會傳達過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思念是永遠不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓兒丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想無論何時都和你這樣的女神在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.28,0:20:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.74,0:20:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有反應了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 如償所願了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了 聲音認證
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認契約
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.35,0:20:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德的偷窺還是有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:20:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.95,0:21:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要你感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀兒德更是什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:10.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.50,0:21:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…開玩笑的
